{"tid":785130,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解女朋友變成錦","createTime":"2018-08-19T03:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T14:53:34.000Z","uid":118188,"like":1,"dislike":198,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"83194f0196b611fa310f1cd911c5bbe762433fb4","tid":785130,"uid":118188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:01:31.000Z","msg":"同女朋友由大學果時拍拖有兩年幾，一開始大家都好好日日都有揾對方，直到佢開始返工時所有野都變曬，whatsapp 少揾我，日日係ig post同其他同事平時返工嘅相搞到我好妒忌佢班同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。佢放假我要早一個星期預約定，如果唔係佢會約朋友同同事去食飯都唔約我先。之前一直都有同佢傾開呢個話題，但係佢反駁話佢好耐冇見啲朋友，我冇野好講。平時溝通方面，whatsapp 要等大半日先回一次，我就當佢忙所以就等佢放工先直接打比佢傾下電話，但係最近佢突然又話唔中意傾電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，姐係咩意思呢？我一直好愛我女朋友同信得過，但係我係佢心目中嘅位置究竟係點，有冇人可以解答下"},{"pid":"ee728d1ac91ea35304a7598e3ca54b9f84ab8b04","tid":785130,"uid":201581,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:02:28.000Z","msg":"帽事既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db14d5f2afebfe2b59b546f73dfda879e994274","tid":785130,"uid":151664,"like":362,"dislike":4,"score":358,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:02:54.000Z","msg":"變成錦鯉？"},{"pid":"dc9fe0d35f4546981130916330ebec972dda03eb","tid":785130,"uid":32722,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:03:26.000Z","msg":"真係好，一早可以護下眼"},{"pid":"1ff15c51e55c96beecb5ca9468aa13207a30a8bb","tid":785130,"uid":29675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537c336a5a9c8f82d2609d4970a27b89b60864a6","tid":785130,"uid":160378,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:05:28.000Z","msg":"認真 一係識咗第二個 一係就唔想再同你一齊"},{"pid":"0b5f28e0bc67650026175110708fe755d5da50ad","tid":785130,"uid":522,"like":15,"d