晒準備飛你 咁你就唔會比佢殺到一個措手不及<br />\n第三。唔出聲 當無事 繼續單方面付出 等佢玩夠 或者 佢頂唔順你仲未出聲<br />\n<br />\n我就係人板。我果陣係用左第一個方法 最後比佢講到係我逼佢同我分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T08:03:32.000Z","msg":"第二振夫剛啦<br />\n你條垃圾應該都做咗下把好耐"},{"pid":"164c7f16af7b591ec3de461713a88c89e390b806","tid":785130,"uid":11328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T08:27:07.000Z","msg":"你條女變左塊布？"},{"pid":"972f1646b99c77f42cbe0252baf78df9e560e5d8","tid":785130,"uid":71181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T08:33:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"811140de8cd2984dc5ba38dc95bbf0dd5044a07a","tid":785130,"uid":24696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T08:53:58.000Z","msg":"我出賣呀錦"},{"pid":"3cc5e81a8ca283b73c7ec43dac513f1ab18bf3d2","tid":785130,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf3e02f79bc123420a30276fd874e9fd65273f5d","tid":785130,"uid":118188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59172ae9b8921b842b46dda8afeaa6d9060970d0","tid":785130,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:36:02.000Z","msg":"佢做咩行業先"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:40:31.000Z","msg":"酒店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T09:18:21.000Z","msg":"酒店啲姐姐好撚索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n去親酒店啲人得幾款，你自己諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e9962fe1fdf8b41cc830c6058741e0cca36ca1","tid":785130,"uid":16241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf3e02f79bc123420a30276fd874e9fd65273f5d","tid":785130,"uid":118188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59172ae9b8921b842b46dda8afeaa6d9060970d0","tid":785130,"uid":7248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:36:02.000Z","msg":"佢做咩行業先"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T03:40:31.000Z","ms